00:22:29,640 --> 00:22:33,561
Look like a mountain

214
00:22:37,482 --> 00:22:39,525
Shadow Clone Jutsu!

215
00:22:39,609 --> 00:22:41,861
Take this!
Fang Over Fang!

216
00:22:41,944 --> 00:22:43,988
Byakugan!

217
00:22:44,614 --> 00:22:47,116
That damn spider bastard!

218
00:22:47,200 --> 00:22:49,410
Me, Naruto, Kiba and Neji.
Our careful planning is not working!

219
00:22:49,494 --> 00:22:52,872
If we dawdle Sasuke will be gone!

220
00:22:52,955 --> 00:22:54,499
Hey, what should we do?!

221
00:22:54,582 --> 00:22:57,668
If we want to continue our pursuit,
there's only one way to do it!

222
